### Predict — unlabeled inference (no ground-truth, no accuracy field)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Classification/Predict
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "samples": [
    { "features": [18,  0.70, 9, 6, 5, 4, 0.50, 3.0] },
    { "features": [300, 0.02, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0.00, 7.1] }
  ]
}

